		"  Clean this mess up!"
		""
		"   I told you two to keep him quiet, not cut out his tongue. Was that really necessary? You couldn't just gag him? It's already difficult enough to keep them all under control without them having to hear the screams of a man having his tongue severed. Your poor mother must have dropped you two on your heads when you were little troll babies."
