readables/man2/journal_hales
{
	precache
	"num_pages"	: "2"
	"page1_left_title"	:
	{
		""
	}
	"page1_left_body"	:
	{
		""
		"    That old taffer Twistleton is right, it's no coincidence Captain Williams arrived right after we caught that thief, Jacobs. I must ensure I remain well out of sight while he's here, as he'll certainly remember me. He was always the type. Knew everyone's name and always took an interest. I am no longer a Watch Lieutenant, but I do remember Captain Williams."
		"We had better watch our step around him. The man is no fool."
		""
		" "
	}
	"page1_right_title"	:
	{
		""
	}
	"page1_right_body"	:
	{
		""
		"   Thankfully I am in agreement with Twistleton's \"order\" to lock the Daltons down the pit. Those two morons are on very thin ice with me, especially after what they did to the thief. Although his attempt to blackjack one of the Dalton brothers was surely an exceptional stupidity. Could he not tell their heads are filled with rocks? I am certain he must have lifted their key, however. One wonders if Williams had anything to do with that? I had better be "
	}
	"page2_left_title"	:
	{
		""
	}
	"page2_left_body"	:
	{
		""
		"on my toes, since there's every possibility he might attempt to make his way down here."
		""
		"   And what an inopportune time for Roland to have absconded. I'm disappointed, for he seemed the most reliable of this pitiable bunch. Thomas informs me that he saw him coming from the direction of the hallway the last time a new group was herded through, apparently looking very sorry for himself. He then locked himself"
	}
	"page2_right_title"	:
	{
		""
	}
	"page2_right_body"	:
	{
		""
		"away with a crate of Ingleby's wine, though where he went thereafter is still unknown."
		"In the meantime I have handed his cooking duties over to Thomas, whose endless complaints on the matter are not doing him any favours. "
	}
	"gui_page1"	: "guis/readables/books/book_calig_summertime.gui"
	"gui_page2"	: "guis/readables/books/book_calig_summertime.gui"
	"snd_page_turn"	: "readable_page_turn"
}


